<h3>How does Fitminder work?</h3>
<p>Fitminder monitors your Fitbit activity to identify periods of time when you haven't moved. When Fitminder sees that you've been sedentary for too long, you'll receive a text message to remind you to get up and move. Fitminder works best when your Fitbit is configured for all-day sync on your mobile device. The more frequently your Fitbit syncs, the more accurate and timely your reminders will be.</p>

